name: Biao on BNBChain
description: WHAT IS $BIAO? The comic originated with Wang Nima, the pseudonymous creator of Baozou Manhua, a rage comic-style webtoon site founded in 2008. LONGEST LASTING MEME Wang's website has rapidly grown, boasting nearly 9 million Weibo fans and nearly a billion video views. It now features popular actors, including Chinese singer Jacky Cheung. the “pepe” of china Like Pepe, $BIAO has been around for a decade, evoking nostalgia as a timeless meme. While Pepe dominated the West with its humor and adaptations, $BIAO now does the same in China. THE BNB CHain $BIAO, a legendary Chinese meme, is thriving on the BNB Chain, which is dominated by Chinese traders. With deep cultural relevance, it's becoming the "Pepe of the East."
